  "detailed_description": "Blending the deep buildcrafting of Action-RPGs like <strong>Path of Exile</strong> and <strong>Diablo</strong> with the fast-paced action of roguelite like <strong>Hades</strong>, Striving for Light is an action RPG where you expand and shape a unique infinite skilltree. Battle through dark, ever-changing worlds, collect powerful loot, craft and upgrade weapons to legendary power, and unlock new characters, skills, and weapons as you strive to conquer the darkness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/1eb0568b53fc63fe25894468ddcc2ec6.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/1eb0568b53fc63fe25894468ddcc2ec6.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/1eb0568b53fc63fe25894468ddcc2ec6.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dive into a dark, mysterious world filled with danger and a voice-acted story<br></li><li>Explore random generated maps with plenty of world events and secrets to uncover<br></li><li>Level up, utilise and shape a unique random generated and infinite expanding skilltree<br></li><li>Near infinite possibilites of buildcrafting and bring your dreambuilds to life<br></li><li>Master 8 character classes each with their own unique specialisation skilltree<br></li><li>Hunt for randomised loot, craft and reforge weapons to true legendary power<br></li><li>Unlock new skills, weapons, maps and characters<br></li><li>Over 11 unique environments each with unique enemies and bosses to explore<br></li><li>Endgame systems (Rifts, Mapping System, Pinnacle Bosses, Challenges)<br></li><li>Online leaderboards with seasons and private league system<br></li><li>Local-Coop mode<br></li><li>Hardcore and Normal mode as well as 5 Difficulty Tiers<br></li><li>Hand-drawn world and an 80+ minute soundtrack</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/dfc08edadf59818f2675b5dc843d76a5.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/dfc08edadf59818f2675b5dc843d76a5.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/dfc08edadf59818f2675b5dc843d76a5.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skill system</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each run gives you a new unique skill tree to explore<br></li><li>Combine melee, ranged and more, like pet skills, for nearly infinite builds<br></li><li>Dynamic expanding skilltree depending on your skill pathway<br></li><li>Collect skillgems and shape your skilltree: Reconnect, reroll, refund.<br></li><li>Additional meta progression skilltree</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/459f171142a146e981d05ac816080d64.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/459f171142a146e981d05ac816080d64.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/459f171142a146e981d05ac816080d64.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gearing & Crafting</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Deep itemisation system <br></li><li>72+ unique weapon bases with randomised stats can be upgraded to legendaries and ascended by crafting <br></li><li>Over 40+ unique trinkets including powerful legendary trinkets <br></li><li>70+ unique skill nodes<br></li><li>8 characters with unique specialisation skilltrees</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/138a2fe19686465482edf4996c231cd3.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/138a2fe19686465482edf4996c231cd3.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/138a2fe19686465482edf4996c231cd3.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat system</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenging enemies and boss encounters<br></li><li>Active dual combat system with aim & attack (mouse, keys or controller)<br></li><li>Dynamically switch between melee and ranged weapons during fights<br></li><li>Powerful active abilities like shapeshifting and massive AoE attacks<br></li><li>Dual resource system to manage melee and ranged attacks<br></li><li>Dodge system to evade enemy attacks</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/e78c2b76585217516e228ce5ed4b38c3.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/e78c2b76585217516e228ce5ed4b38c3.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/e78c2b76585217516e228ce5ed4b38c3.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endgame system</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Delve deeper into the darkness and face an ever increasing challenge<br></li><li>Infinite expanding map progression system<br></li><li>Rift Endgame system<br></li><li>5 Difficulty Tiers<br></li><li>Add and alter map modifiers to increase the challenge but also your rewards</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/aec12ec5e642a25eebc58426bc5f48d0.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/aec12ec5e642a25eebc58426bc5f48d0.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/aec12ec5e642a25eebc58426bc5f48d0.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seasons & Leaderboards</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Seasonal leaderboards for hardcore and softcore mode <br></li><li> Earn honour points for each run and climb the seasonal leaderboard<br></li><li> Compete in seasonal challenges<br></li><li> Leaderboard for pinnacle boss fight rush<br></li><li> Rift endgame leaderboards<br></li><li> Offline mode</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/b8935d2141d7ce2fa264b73f32afe963.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/b8935d2141d7ce2fa264b73f32afe963.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/b8935d2141d7ce2fa264b73f32afe963.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Generated Worlds</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each map layout is procedural generated<br></li><li> Ever changing world events like tower defense, arenas, dungeons, trials, and bossfights<br></li><li> Wisely choose which maps to play and which world events to engage<br></li><li> Hunt for the perfect loot and the ultimate weapons</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/f1ba93d02b2666d20511987903dda105.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=614 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/f1ba93d02b2666d20511987903dda105.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/f1ba93d02b2666d20511987903dda105.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leave a Legacy</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Craft echo weapons that get added to the lootpool for other players to find<br></li><li> Empower your echoes, design the visual appearance of your weapons<br></li><li> Embed your personal inscription to share your message with other players</li></ul><br><br>",
