er into the darkness and face an ever increasing challenge<br></li><li>Infinite expanding map progression system<br></li><li>Rift Endgame system<br></li><li>5 Difficulty Tiers<br></li><li>Add and alter map modifiers to increase the challenge but also your rewards</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/aec12ec5e642a25eebc58426bc5f48d0.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/aec12ec5e642a25eebc58426bc5f48d0.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/aec12ec5e642a25eebc58426bc5f48d0.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seasons & Leaderboards</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Seasonal leaderboards for hardcore and softcore mode <br></li><li> Earn honour points for each run and climb the seasonal leaderboard<br></li><li> Compete in seasonal challenges<br></li><li> Leaderboard for pinnacle boss fight rush<br></li><li> Rift endgame leaderboards<br></li><li> Offline mode</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/b8935d2141d7ce2fa264b73f32afe963.poster.avif?t=1753540771\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/b8935d2141d7ce2fa264b73f32afe963.webm?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/b8935d2141d7ce2fa264b73f32afe963.mp4?t=1753540771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Generated Worlds</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each map layout is proc